      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>Literary Photography was born from a simple belief: that the most powerful stories emerge when words and images dance together. This space exists at the intersection of literature and visual art, where each photograph carries a narrative and every story paints a picture.</p>
      
      <p>In a world increasingly divided between the written word and the visual medium, we believe there's profound beauty in their union. Here, you'll find literary works that may be accompanied by carefully chosen photographs, and photographic stories that speak as eloquently as any written piece.</p>

      <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
