      <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
      <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #667eea; padding-left: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; font-style: italic; color: #4b5563; font-size: 1.125rem;">
        "Every photograph is a story waiting to be told, and every story is a world waiting to be seen."
      </blockquote>
      
      <p>We believe that literature and photography are not competing forms of expression, but complementary languages that can amplify each other's impact. A photograph can illuminate the emotional landscape of a poem, while a well-crafted sentence can reveal layers of meaning in a visual composition.</p>

      <h2>About the Creator</h2>
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f9fafb 0%, #f3f4f6 100%); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin: 2rem 0;">
        <p>This project is the work of a writer and photographer who believes in the power of thoughtful, intentional content. With a background in both literary arts and visual storytelling, the goal is to create a space where these passions can coexist and enrich each other.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">When not behind the camera or at the keyboard, you can find the creator exploring the quiet moments that often hold the most profound stories‚Äîwhether that's the way light falls across an old building, or the rhythm of words in an overheard conversation.</p>
      </div>

